%EDITMAC  ------------------ UCASE     MACRO  ------------------------
%COMMAND ===>_ZCMD
+
+THE%UCASE+MACRO IS USED TO CONVERT THE ENTIRE DATASET TO UPPER-CASE.
+
+USE:
+TYPE%UCASE+ON THE COMMAND LINE
+
%COMMAND ===> UCASE A
+***************************** TOP OF DATA *****************************
+000001  Data line 1
+000002  Data line 2
+000003  Data line 3
+000004  Data line 4
%RESULT:
+***************************** TOP OF DATA *****************************
+000001  DATA LINE 1
+000002  DATA LINE 2
+000003  DATA LINE 3
+000004  DATA LINE 4
)PROC
&KEY = .PFKEY
)END
